{"tid":2319740,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"FB被控違反壟斷法　被要求強制拆售IG WhatsApp","createTime":"2020-12-10T09:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T13:50:03.000Z","uid":141151,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"f1f693f3aab35b3c9f0695e1d4ea16117e01fbd5","tid":2319740,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:49:30.000Z","msg":"FB被控違反壟斷法　被要求強制拆售IG WhatsApp<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416077\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416077&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpgqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=c2a15d64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416077&h=d34ed0f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416077</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國聯邦貿易委員會聯同48個州及地區，控告Facebook違反反壟斷法，要求強制拆售Instagram及WhatsApp。Facebook反駁稱，這兩宗收購數年前是經由聯邦貿易委員會審批，又指反壟斷法不應用來懲罰成功的企業。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦貿易委員會、華盛頓特區、美屬關島及46個州的總檢察長周三入稟法院，控告Facebook違反反壟斷法，令Facebook成為繼Alphabet公司旗下的Google，十月被美國司法部起訴後，今年第二間面對反壟斷法訴訟的科網巨企，亦是自1998年「微軟案」後最大的一宗反壟斷法訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n紐約州總檢察長詹樂霞指，Facebook過去近十年一直在市場進行「掠奪行為」，利用其支配地位及壟斷力量打壓其他較小型的競爭者，並會以大量金錢收購競爭對手及潛在的競爭對手。<br />\n<br />\n詹樂霞：「為了維持在社交網絡的市場支配地位，Facebook使用『買或埋』策略阻礙競爭對手。Facebook會嘗試將拒絕被收購的公司任何生存空間扼殺殆盡。」<br />\n<br />\n聯邦貿易委員會亦批評，Facebook利用系統性策略除去競爭對手，訴狀點名指控Facebook違法收購WhatsApp及Instagram，要求採取補救性措施恢復市場信心，包括要求法院下令Facebook剝離資產、拆售WhatsApp及Instagram。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook在2012年及2014年，分別以10億及190億美元收購Instagram及WhatsApp。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook回應指，這兩宗收購交易當年是經由聯邦貿易委員會審批，又指反壟斷法並不是用來懲罰成功的企業，形容有關訴訟屬於「修正主義歷史」；強調Instagram及WhatsApp取得成功，是因為Facebook投入了數以十億美元資金發展。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook是全球最大的社交網絡，目前用戶數目多達27億，公司市值近8千億美元。"},{"pid":"ed027e2927cc3739f822c1abf91e889d7ccc5dc2","tid":2319740,"uid":21896,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:52:20.000Z","msg":"Dklm我響wtsapp打過nike acg,我睇fb個時佢彈啲買nike acg既廣告俾我"},{"pid":"eb7424c60a44ce891da3d60e73dd7930464b824a","tid":2319740,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:53:15.000Z","msg":"呢個state attorney general點解咁正常既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又起訴big tech 之前又禁止blm籌款"},{"pid":"08da124914cb56651247a184a2dfc8d8475669dd","tid":2319740,"uid":39365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:54:41.000Z","msg":"幾時到google"},{"pid":"04aeeb5f81893a37b4a1ee8b6a52be4ceed06ba8","tid":2319740,"uid":8918,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ed027e2927cc3739f822c1abf91e889d7ccc5dc2","tid":2319740,"uid":21896,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:52:20.000Z","msg":"Dklm我響wtsapp打過nike acg,我睇fb個時佢彈啲買nike acg既廣告俾我"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:54:46.000Z","msg":"其實佢控晒呢3間係有啲屈機<br />\n同已經好大程度控制左IM 市場"},{"pid":"d79f3720c85ea0af2081254bdec587cd0df1f767","tid":2319740,"uid":254450,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:55:08.000Z","msg":"facebook老嘢先用，割走ig同whatsapp之後嘅facebook我都想睇吓佢點走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a614fcb9666f7855329b3e24b634fe8d6d429ae","tid":2319740,"uid":278219,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:55:52.000Z","msg":"最應該就拆9 google."},{"pid":"80001fac18db2d894a04bd3e36932009e6a91670","tid":2319740,"uid":275724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1f693f3aab35b3c9f0695e1d4ea16117e01fbd5","tid":2319740,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:49:30.000Z","msg":"FB被控違反壟斷法　被要求強制拆售IG WhatsApp<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416077\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416077&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpgqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=c2a15d64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/fr